OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780413074
OL,3,CFamily of builder who fell three
OL,4,Cstoreys urge people to take care when
OL,5,Cdoing DIY
OL,7,FThe family of a builder from Bristol
OL,8,Fwho received brain damage and severe
OL,9,Finjuries after falling from a ladder
OL,10,Fare urging people to take care when
OL,11,Fdoing DIY projects.
OL,13,FScott Blankley, who's 47, broke 11
OL,14,Fribs and suffered a brain bleed, lung
OL,15,Fand kidney damage after falling three
OL,16,Fstoreys while painting an external
OL,17,Fwall on 17 January 2026.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
