FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780413074
OL,3,CFamily of builder who fell three
OL,4,Cstoreys urge people to take care when
OL,5,Cdoing DIY
OL,7,FPart of his skull was recently
OL,8,Freplaced with a metal plate after it
OL,9,Fhad to be removed to allow for his
OL,10,Fbrain swelling.
OL,12,FHis brother Kai said although Scott
OL,13,Fworked in the building trade, doing a
OL,14,Fproject at home may have meant he
OL,15,Fwasn't thinking as seriously about his
OL,16,Fsafety.
OL,18,F"This is what he does, day in day out.
OL,19,FI guess at home you don't take the
OL,20,Fsame precautions, you probably skip a
OL,21,Ffew steps," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780413074
OL,3,CFamily of builder who fell three
OL,4,Cstoreys urge people to take care when
OL,5,Cdoing DIY
OL,7,F"There was no one at the bottom of the
OL,8,Fladder looking after it, he wasn't
OL,9,Fattached to it. There are a few things
OL,10,Fhe should have done that in hindsight
OL,11,Fprobably could have saved him."
OL,13,FThe No Falls Foundation, a charity
OL,14,Fdedicated to preventing falls from
OL,15,Fheight, has warned that the number of
OL,16,Faccidents linked to DIY is increasing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780413074
OL,3,CFamily of builder who fell three
OL,4,Cstoreys urge people to take care when
OL,5,Cdoing DIY
OL,7,FMore than 40,000 people were injured
OL,8,Fwhen falling from height last year at
OL,9,Fwork, but the charity says this hides
OL,10,Fthe "hidden crisis" of falls and near
OL,11,Fmisses in the home.
OL,13,F"These type of accidents can happen in
OL,14,Fthe blink of an eye," said Hannah
OL,15,FWilliams from the No Falls Foundation.
OL,17,F"It could be somebody overreaching, or
OL,18,Fnot using the right kind of equipment,
OL,19,Fbut things can get quite serious quite
OL,20,Fquickly."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780413074
OL,3,CFamily of builder who fell three
OL,4,Cstoreys urge people to take care when
OL,5,Cdoing DIY
OL,7,FAs summer approaches, and people may
OL,8,Fattempt more DIY work in their homes,
OL,9,Fthey advise people to think twice
OL,10,Fbefore getting started.
OL,12,F"Think about the task ahead, make sure
OL,13,Fthat you're competent to do it, make
OL,14,Fsure that you have the right equipment
OL,15,Ffor that job, and don't take
OL,16,Funnecessary risks because things can
OL,17,Fgo wrong very quickly," Hannah said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
